name: .ALZ File Extension
summary: Learn about .ALZ files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Proprietary compressed file format developed by ESTsoft; uses an algorithm similar to .ZIP compression, but is optimized for compressing large archives; also supports self-extracting and spanned archives.

content: ALZ files can be decompressed by ALZip, which is part of the ALTools PC utility suite and is also available as a standalone product.
